data.description: Amazing investment opportunity! This single, detached 3-bedroom 2-bath fixer-upper sits on a 1/4 acre, 10,000 Sqft. lot. Also features an enclosed front porch and a semi-finished attic that could be used as an additional bedroom, gym, or home office. The property is situated on a corner lot, located on a quiet neighborhood street just minutes away from PHL, I-95 and I-76. Very convenient to public transportation, parks and shopping centers. The upcoming Bellwether District, which will be located just a few miles away at the old PES refinery, will create upwards of 80,000 jobs creating a demand for near-by housing. Investors and builders have the option of removing existing structure to create a blank canvas to build a multi-unit residential building. The Bellwether District, a 1,300-acre state-of-the-art campus will be Philly's new home for e-commerce, life sciences, and logistics leaders transforming South and Southwest Philadelphia. Get ahead of the game and check out the potential that this property has to offer!
